<div id="I_file">&lt;cstdio&gt;</div>
<h1>BUFSIZ</h1>
<div id="I_description">Buffer size</div>
<section id="description">
This macro constant expands to an integral expression with the size of the buffer used by the <a href="/setbuf">setbuf</a> function.<br>
</section>
